translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,17,"Ẹ̀yin kọ́ l’ẹ pa wọ́n, ṣùgbọ́n Allāhu l’Ó pa wọ́n. Àti pé ìwọ kọ́ l’o jùkò nígbà tí o jùkò, àmọ́ dájúdájú Allāhu l’Ó jùkò nítorí kí (Allāhu) lè fi àmìwò dáadáa kan àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ ni. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Olùgbọ́, Onímọ̀"
  8,18,Ìyẹn (báyẹn). Dájúdájú Allāhu máa sọ ète àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ di lílẹ
  8,19,"Tí ẹ̀yin (aláìgbàgbọ́) bá ń wá ìdájọ́, dájúdájú ìdájọ́ ti kò le yín lórí. Tí ẹ bá jáwọ́ (níbi ogun), ó sì dára jùlọ fun yín. Tí ẹ bá tún padà (síbi ogun), A máa padà (ran àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo lọ́wọ́); àkójọ yín kò sì níí rọ̀ yín lọ́rọ̀ kan kan, ìbáà pọ̀. Dájúdájú Allāhu ń bẹ pẹ̀lú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo"
  8,20,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ tẹ̀lé ti Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀. Ẹ má ṣe gbúnrí kúrò ní ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ̀ nígbà tí ẹ bá ń gbọ́ (āyah) lọ́wọ́"
  8,21,"Ẹ má se dà bí àwọn tí wọ́n wí pé: “A gbọ́.” Wọn kò sì gbọ́"
  8,22,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀dá abẹ̀mí t’ó burú jùlọ ní ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu ni àwọn adití, ayaya tí kò ṣe làákàyè"
  8,23,"Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé Allāhu mọ oore kan lára wọn ni, ìbá jẹ́ kí wọ́n gbọ́. Tí (Allāhu) bá sì fún wọn gbọ́ ni, dájúdájú wọn máa pẹ̀yìn dà, wọn yó sì máa gbúnrí"
  8,24,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ jẹ́pè ti Allāhu àti ti Òjíṣẹ́, nígbà tí ó bá pè yín síbi n̄ǹkan tí ó máa mu yín ṣẹ̀mí. Kí ẹ sì mọ̀ pé dájúdájú Allāhu ń ṣèdíwọ́ láààrin ènìyàn àti ọkàn rẹ̀. Dájúdájú ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ sì ni wọ́n máa ko yín jọ sí"
  8,25,Ẹ ṣọrá fún àdánwò kan tí kò níí mọ lórí àwọn t’ó ṣàbòsí nínú yín nìkan. Kí ẹ sì mọ̀ pé dájúdájú Allāhu le níbi ìyà